{"tid":2400602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸戰線｜緬甸人民、人權組織批評中國包庇緬甸軍政府","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T16:15:36.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b33d6c1c0b9825fa94cfc600eff3d16b7fc3a35","tid":2400602,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3415261118612839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoseph.lo.1840%2Fposts%2F3415261118612839&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=57077fa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joseph.lo.1840/posts/3415261118612839</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJpDZJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJpDZJM.jpg&h=1e934d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Joseph Lo<br />\n<br />\n【<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t1e/1/16/1f1f2_1f1f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft1e%2F1%2F16%2F1f1f2_1f1f2.png&h=d2c170b2&s={SIZE}\" />緬甸戰線｜緬甸人民、人權組織批評中共包庇緬甸軍政府】<br />\n<br />\n緬甸全國連續三日出現大型示威，譴責軍隊發動軍事政變奪權，其中首都內比都黑警以水砲驅散群眾，令局勢再度升溫。鑑於中共早前拖延安理會譴責聲明，人權組織「Human Rights Watch」 聯合國事務主管Louis Charbonneau發出公開呼籲，要求中共立即停止包庇緬甸軍政府的行為。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會雖然召開緊急會議，但因中俄堅持要獲得他們同意，才能發表聲明，終令安理會沒有發表聲明。<br />\n<br />\nLouis Charbonneau批評中共長期與緬甸及軍隊有密切關係，認為其他成員須向緬甸及中共發出強烈信息，向緬甸實施武器禁運，並針對軍隊高層採取入境禁令及凍結資產。他又警告，一旦中共否決的話，中共要為其行為及後果向世界做出交代。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是，不少緬甸網民認同相關建議，直言中共包庇軍政府、打壓緬甸民主，#ShameOnChina 成為熱門hashtag之一，亦有聲音批評中共黨媒加入抺黑緬甸抗爭，表示緬甸人上街純粹因為網禁，與爭取民主無關。<br />\n<br />\n這意味緬甸人開始看清中共的遺害，當中共包庇緬甸軍政府之際，香港更加應該支持「奶茶聯盟」的盟友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Hello_helloMM/status/1358627505125675009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHello_helloMM%2Fstatus%2F1358627505125675009&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=3d64cdd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHello_helloMM%2Fstatus%2F1358627505125675009&h=136a8f33\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Hello_helloMM/status/1358627505125675009</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hrw/status/1358579197527097346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhrw%2Fstatus%2F1358579197527097346&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=1e15131f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhrw%2Fstatus%2F1358579197527097346&h=5ca14a3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hrw/status/1358579197527097346</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hrw.org/news/2021/02/05/time-call-chinas-bluff-myanmar-un\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2021%2F02%2F05%2Ftime-call-chinas-bluff-myanmar-un&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=8ec1c81a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hrw.org/news/2021/02/05/time-call-chinas-bluff-myanmar-un</a>"},{"pid":"897122569537f8bbe3aec6e913852db0c2442219","tid":2400602,"uid":19557,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"好機會 借今次將支拿向世界標籤為邪惡軸心 等佢一直做既大外宣白廢功夫"},{"pid":"8f63ef546cba2174bfcfbd7a24671249513f8b78","tid":2400602,"uid":82394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"897122569537f8bbe3aec6e913852db0c2442219","tid":2400602,"uid":19557,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"好機會 借今次將支拿向世界標籤為邪惡軸心 等佢一直做既大外宣白廢功夫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"佢哋做得越嚟越出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c2429c02f7236f4c116bfa89bfd6c12f954e4e","tid":2400602,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8f63ef546cba2174bfcfbd7a24671249513f8b78","tid":2400602,"uid":82394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8